{
  "text": "Many other antibodies have been associated with AIP but are not diagnostic and include antibodies to carbonic anhydrase II antigens and lactoferrin [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] , as well as rheumatoid factor, antinuclear antibody, and anti-smooth muscle antibody [CITATION_3] .",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "24429655",
